#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:407
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_SURRENDER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不，继续战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:413
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们击败了诡异的方碑守卫，其货舱内的物品想必已尽数毁坏。正欲离开时，你们发现"
"一件奇特的装置竟在战斗中幸存：这是个似乎能解析守卫所用古老语言的翻译器。看来"
"这片星域被一个名为\"联合方碑\"的集团控制着。要是战前就有这个设备该多好……\n"
"\n"
"\t你们同时扫描了星域，发现在星域核心处出现与来时传送门相同的巨大能量波动。若"
"存在离开的途径，这很可能就是你们的出路。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:419
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_DESTROY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:424
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们击败了诡异的方碑守卫。由于舰上已无船员阻挠，你们得以搜查其货舱，找到一件"
"奇特的蓝色武器，以及一个似乎能解析守卫所用古老语言的翻译器。看来这片星域被名"
"为\"联合方碑\"的集团控制着。要是战前就有这个设备该多好……\n"
"\n"
"\t在货舱里，你们还发现指向星域内特定坐标的星图，标记着被称为\"出口\"的裂隙。"
"若想离开此地，那里似乎就是你们的目的地。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:431
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_DEADCREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:440
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_FOLLOWUP\"]/text"
msgstr "既然击杀了联合方碑的守卫，他们必定会派出增援部队追捕你们。在探索这片星域时，请务必步步为营。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:443
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_FOLLOWUP\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:447
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_COMMONWEALTH_FOLLOWUP\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:456
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_COMMONWEALTH\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:457
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_COMMONWEALTH\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "已探索的信标，没什么值得注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:458
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_COMMONWEALTH\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:460
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们瞥见一艘动力强劲的联合方碑舰船，但对方显然对你们充满敌意。\"外来者！竟敢摧毁我们的守卫！准备承受我们的怒火吧！\"该舰迅速发起攻击，你们很快意识到这正是因袭击事件而被派来追剿你们的守卫舰之一。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:464
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:496
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这个星区本应是你和船员的避风港，但自从叛军袭击及随后的星联入侵以来，这里已沦"
"为无人地带。更糟的是，海盗们也被吸引到此地，企图轻松搜刮废料。步步为营，时刻"
"保持警惕。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:504
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:506
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"看来星联设法抽调出了一艘精锐护卫舰，以阻止此星区获得任何增援，无论这些增援来"
"自叛军还是联邦。“那么，你们就是他们派来试图与我们对战的增援？真可爱。告诉我，"
"哦，那艘‘能行’的联邦船，你们指望如何仅凭一道孤零零的屏障来阻挡无尽的浪潮？”话"
"音落下，护卫舰的武器随之启动。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:508
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:510
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你将武器锁定那艘护卫舰，逼近并发起攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:513
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:519
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_mantis_queen\"]/text"
msgstr "（莱孔普利纳克拉）莱孔普利纳克拉要求自由通行！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:521
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_mantis_queen\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你竟敢用这种态度跟你的女王说话？立刻放我们过去，否则我亲手将你公开处决。听明"
"白了吗？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t卫兵一见到女王，慌忙立正致敬。“当……当然，陛下！这边请！”卫兵随即放"
"行，还送来了一些补给，并通知联盟舰队准许你们通过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:528
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "（七夜）七夜要求自由通行！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:530
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你给我听好了，你这不中用的士兵！立刻放我们过去，否则我就让你成为星联的头号敌"
"人！”\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t守卫愣了片刻，随即关掉了武器。“行吧，舰长。我这就通知舰队。”守卫还"
"给你们送来了一些补给。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:537
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/text"
msgstr "（泰迪奥）要求自由通行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:539
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“请恕我打扰。我是泰迪奥，共和国总统。作为星联的领导人之一，我想在此礼貌地请求"
"安全通行权。”\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t那名守卫歪了歪头，随后耸了耸肩。“好吧，总统先生。我会立刻通知舰队。"
"”这名守卫还向你发送了一些补给。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:546
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_CREW_RUES\"]/text"
msgstr "（团结精英精英船员）试着说服他们让你通过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:548
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_CREW_RUES\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“看来我完全搞错了。你绝不可能是联邦的船，尤其船上还有我们的一名精英士兵。你可"
"以通过了。”守卫将注意力转回叛军身上，不过在此之前，还是先给你送来了一些补给品"
"作为支援。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:553
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）向舰队要求援助。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:562
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION_VANCE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"万斯切入当地MFK舰队通讯所使用的特定频率，清了清嗓子。\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t“士兵们！我是万斯本尊！所有能投入战斗的部队立刻报到，给我攻击挡路的星联守卫"
"！”\n"
"\n"
"\t那名星联守卫放声大笑：“哦，拜托！你的部队正节节败退，你以为他们还有人手来帮"
"你？怪不得叛军快完——”星联舰长的话说到一半便戛然而止，入侵警报开始在敌舰上响彻"
"不绝。看来那支舰队里还真腾得出几个MFK王牌精英！不过，这也没能阻止守卫转而攻击"
"你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:569
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_COALITION_VANCE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:581
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr "守卫舰似乎正在向附近的反舰炮台发出求救信号！准备应对冲击！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:583
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
msgstr "（信号稀释器）阻塞对方通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:585
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当没有反舰炮台激活时，你认为这是一个好兆头，说明你的增强部件功能正常，于是你"
"继续战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:589
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:591
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "突然，你侦测到远处那支叛军舰队调转了炮口，现在正指向那名星联守卫！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:599
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你已击败星联守卫。无论他们船上曾载有何种货物，此刻都必定已化为乌有，但你好歹"
"还能从残骸中打捞出一些补给。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:602
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_DESTROY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:607
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你已击败星联守卫。船上已无船员阻拦，你可以搜查他们的货舱。你找到一件武器带回"
"飞船，接着开始拆解他们的船体。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:611
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_DEADCREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:619
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_FOLLOWUP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你摧毁了星联守卫舰，这无疑已经让他们派出增援来追捕你。在探索这个星区时，务必"
"小心行事。不过，鉴于这个星区眼下混乱不堪，这里的部队可能自顾不暇，顾不上管你"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:628
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_FOLLOWUP\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:632
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_COALITION_FOLLOWUP\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:640
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:641
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "已探索的信标，没什么值得注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:642
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:644
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"“我们要把你们这些联邦渣滓碾成碎片！你们会后悔来到此地！”一艘敌对的星联精英舰"
"船逼近，你怀疑他们的怒火远不止来自死去的守卫。\n"
"\n"
"然而，战斗尚未真正打响，你便侦测到远处的联邦舰队也已将炮口对准了这艘星联舰船"
"。现在，全面混战正式爆发！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:653
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:662
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:663
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "已探索的信标，没什么值得注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:664
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "未去过的位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:666
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"“我们要把你们这些联邦渣滓碾成碎片！你们会后悔来到此地！”一艘敌对的星联精英舰"
"船逼近，你怀疑他们的怒火远不止来自死去的守卫。\n"
"\n"
"\t然而，战斗尚未真正打响，你便侦测到远处的联邦舰队也已将炮口对准了这艘星联舰"
"船。现在，全面混战正式爆发！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:677
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_COALITION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:690
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这个星区本应是你和船员的避风港，但自从叛军袭击及随后的星联入侵以来，这里已沦"
"为无人地带。更糟的是，海盗们也被吸引到此地，企图轻松搜刮废料。步步为营，时刻"
"保持警惕。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:698
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:700
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"看来叛军设法牢牢守住了星区入口，甚至还有一名MFK王牌守卫驻守在此。他们立刻发现"
"了你，并启动了武器和火炮。“哦，当然，一个该死的变元者偏要往这浑水里插一脚，我"
"们现在已经够焦头烂额的了，最不需要的就是再多一条联邦的狗来找麻烦！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:702
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:704
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你将武器锁定那艘护卫舰，逼近并发起攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:713
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）“立正，士兵！立即解除武装，准予我们通行！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:715
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦，该死！是万斯本尊！很-很抱歉误会了，我们把你识别成联邦军了！我们会通知舰"
"队尽可能帮你，但眼下我们自己也忙得不可开交，抽不出太多人手。你要是有空，帮我"
"们多送几艘星联的船去见阎王！”这名MFK王牌守卫关闭了武器，发出安全信号，同时惊"
"险地躲过了一发ASB炮击。随后，他传送了一名MFK士兵登船，为你的旅途助阵。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:720
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_vance_one\"]/text"
msgstr "（万斯本尊）“立正，士兵！立即解除武装，准予我们通行！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:722
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_vance_one\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那名MFK王牌守卫眨了眨眼，随即喊道：“本尊？！你在这儿干什么？！就算这会让我上"
"军事法庭我也不管了；在你做了那么多事之后，我们绝不会放你过去！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:725
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_vance_one\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:731
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_cyra\"]/text"
msgstr "（塞拉）“停下，勇敢的士兵！这艘船由一名MFK王牌指挥，立刻关停你的武器！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:733
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_cyra\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"MFK王牌守卫震惊地看到塞拉，匆匆关闭了武器和火炮。“非常抱歉，女士！我们这就把"
"所有能匀出来的补给都发给您，为我们的鲁莽行为致歉！”守卫调拨了几箱补给品，随后"
"便将注意力转回到了星联舰队上。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:738
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_mfk\"]/text"
msgstr "（MFK王牌船员）派这名MFK成员去说服他们放你通行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:740
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_mfk\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“啊，你在执行卧底任务吗？聪明，我相信你接到的任何任务都会为叛军带来一场光荣的"
"胜利！”这MFK王牌守卫大笑起来，给你发送了一些补给作为支援，随后便将注意力转回"
"了正在入侵的星联舰队。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:745
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_JERRY\"]/text"
msgstr "（杰瑞）“你好！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:751
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"REBEL_ID\"]/text"
msgstr "（伪造ID卡）尝试将你的飞船伪装成叛军船只。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:753
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"REBEL_ID\"]/event/text"
msgstr "“你……你真觉得我会吃这套？哇哦……”那名MFK王牌守卫挂断通讯，随即逼近发动攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:756
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"REBEL_ID\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:762
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "（七夜）七夜想说些什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:764
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"七夜轻笑着，又灌了一口啤酒。“说说看，没了你那门厉害的火炮，你打算怎么对付我们"
"？”他按下了藏在背后那个奇怪遥控器上的大红按钮。\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t“什么？你在说什么，你这醉醺醺的蛞蝓？”守卫困惑地问道，话音未落，一"
"声巨大的爆炸便切断了通讯。敌人的火炮暂时瘫痪了，七夜则醉醺醺地狂笑起来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:770
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_REBEL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:791
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_REBEL_SIGNAL\"]/text"
