"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_FEDERATION_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你已击败联邦守卫。船上已无船员阻拦，你可以搜查他们的货舱。你找到一件武器带回"
"飞船，接着开始拆解他们的船体。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1113
