"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_NEBULA_LIGHT_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_FEDERATION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这片星域曾是你和你船员的避风港，但自从叛军袭击以及随后的星联入侵以来，这片星"
"域已变成了无人区。如果这还不够糟的话，海盗们也被吸引到这个地方，希望能轻松捞"
"到废料。小心行事，时刻保持警惕。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1200
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1202
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"令人震惊的是，一群海盗不知何故占领了入口信标。此地原有的联邦抵抗力量几乎可以"
"肯定已被摧毁，使得这些亡命之徒能够随意让任何人进入。当然，叛军和星联对这一结"
"果并不满意，因此一直在竭尽全力试图突破海盗的舰队。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1204
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1206
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"海盗守卫很快向你发出通讯。视频屏幕上，一位高大强壮、手臂上布满伤疤的女性向你"
"打招呼。“啊，我们这儿来了个什么，伙计们？一位变元者？哎呀呀，这在咱们这一带可"
"真少见。还挂着联邦的旗子呢，是吧？好了，别耽误你重要的小旅程了。不过我们可不"
"是谁都会放行的。我相信你很清楚，这片星区有点像个地狱地带。不过嘛，要是你给我"
"们点废料，或许能暂时把我们的注意力从这岗位上引开一会儿。”她发出威胁性的低笑，"
"并眨了眨眼。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1208
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1210
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你将武器锁定那艘护卫舰，逼近并发起攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1213
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "缴纳费用。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1221
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“选得好，小子。”那名海盗点了点头，随即挂断了通讯。既然你已不再挡路，那艘船便"
"迅速前去支援防守了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1228
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/text"
msgstr "（紫胡子）“让我们过去……莎拉……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1230
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她盯着紫胡子看了几秒，随即轻笑一声，摇了摇头。“随你怎么说，老大。拿着，路上用"
"的。”她眨了眨眼，将一件武器和一些补给传送了过来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1236
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "（七夜）七夜要求自由通行！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1238
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“问题就在这儿，伙计。我是七夜船长，我会通过你们的检查站，而且一片废料都不会付"
"。唯一的问题是，我要不要把你们这艘船的船壳也变成我的财富？嗯？我们彼此理解了"
"吗？”\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t守卫咆哮起来，舰船的武器开始充能：“你以为我会在意像你这样的*黏"
"虫*？！你知道吗，去他的贿赂，我要你的*脑袋*！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1246
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_kaz\"]/text"
msgstr "（卡扎卡普勒斯里克）告诉他们，他们眼前正站着一位传奇。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1248
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_kaz\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你们正站在伟大的卡扎卡普勒斯里克·提卡兹帕卡齐卡面前！若还不退下，你们的脑袋"
"就会在你们反应过来之前被我砍落在地！”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t守卫倒抽一口气。“能……能见到您是我的荣幸。当然，您请自便。”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“我还需要些废料，补偿占我的这点时间。你给是不给？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t守卫叹了口气，温顺地点了点头，然后给了这位传奇海盗他想要的东西"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1259
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tuco\"]/text"
msgstr "（图科）恐吓这名守卫。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1261
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tuco\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哈！你以为你这种毛头小子能敲诈得了我——可怖的图科？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“可怖的图科？？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“你给我听好了。我不光是想去哪儿就去哪儿，我还要求你为这番冒犯做"
"出赔偿！”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“是、是，当然，图科。”那名海盗守卫给你送来了一些废料。\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“后会有期。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1274
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_A55\"]/text"
msgstr "（A55）传输访问代码。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1276
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_A55\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"（A55）“哟，看到这通行码没？知道俺是谁不？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“A55舰长？您在这儿有何贵干？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“关你啥事！俺给这地界儿带来了那么多好货，识相的就闪一边儿去，懂"
"？”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“当然，A55。您请便。”\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“走之前再给俺把补给装满！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1289
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_angel\"]/text"
msgstr "（死亡使者）“这艘船受佣兵团授权，可随意通行。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1291
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_angel\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"守卫忙不迭地连声道歉。“当然，当然，请容我们献上一份薄礼。您夺下的这艘船可真是"
"不错。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1309
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr "守卫舰似乎正在向附近的反舰炮台发出求救信号！准备应对冲击！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1311
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
msgstr "（信号稀释器）阻塞对方通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1313
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当没有反舰炮台激活时，你认为这是一个好兆头，说明你的增强部件功能正常，于是你"
"继续战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1317
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1319
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "突然，你侦测到远处星联与MFK的舰队调转了炮口，现在正指向那名海盗守卫！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1327
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你已击败精英海盗守卫。无论他们船上曾载有何种货物，此刻都必定已化为乌有，但你"
"好歹还能从残骸中回收一些补给。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1330
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_DESTROY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1335
